ELLIE LUMME is a medium-length film starring Allison Torem, Stephen Cone, and Mallory Nees. Directed by Ignatiy Vishnevetsky, photographed by Cory Popp, designed & costumed by Theresa Vishnevetskaya, and edited by Shane Simmons, with sound by Stephen Lynch and music by Jacob Trombetta.
